      "text": "\"The Nature of Order\" is the latest book from [[Christopher Alexander]]. More exactly: it is not a single book, it is a four volume (2164 pages) set published by Oxford University Press published 2003-2004. A web page with more information about the book may be found at [http://www.math.utsa.edu/sphere/salingar/NatureofOrder.html www.math.utsa.edu]. Alexander is selling the book online at [http://www.natureoforder.com www.natureoforder.com]. ",
